722720f.title: Manhattan: Riverside Drive - 84th Street
722720f.text:
Riverside Drive, north from West 84th Street, and showing apartment structures on the east side of same, facing Riverside Park. Paralleling the latter is the North (Hudson) River with its Jersey Palisades. In the center of this view, at West 89th Street is the Soldiers and
Sailors Monumint.
January 28, 1938.
George D. Chinn.
